### Create GeoTag (POST /api/geotags)  -> expect 201 + Location header + JSON with id
POST http://localhost:3001/api/geotags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Park",
  "latitude": 49.01,
  "longitude": 8.40,
  "hashtag": "#nature"
}

### Read all GeoTags (GET /api/geotags) -> expect JSON array (contains the new tag)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/geotags

### Read single GeoTag (GET /api/geotags/:id)
# Set the id manually to the value from the Location header (e.g. 12)
@id = 15
GET http://localhost:3001/api/geotags/{{id}}

### Update GeoTag (PUT /api/geotags/:id) -> expect updated JSON with same id
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/geotags/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Park",
  "latitude": 49.02,
  "longitude": 8.41,
  "hashtag": "#updated"
}

### Search GeoTags (GET /api/geotags?...) -> expect filtered JSON array
GET http://localhost:3001/api/geotags?latitude=49.02&longitude=8.41&searchterm=Updated

### Delete GeoTag (DELETE /api/geotags/:id) -> expect deleted JSON (or 200/204 depending on impl)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/geotags/{{id}}

### Verify deletion (GET /api/geotags/:id) -> expect 404
GET http://localhost:3001/api/geotags/{{id}}

